data.text: @lamb83 gwen don't limit yourself.  tina turner performed into her 70's.

@lamb83 Right. I think she needs to just push forward, & change that old narrative. I remember her having a similar issue when she was turning 30 I believe & even though I’m younger than her I even knew then how silly it was let something like a number effect your life

@gregory_scepi I agree! I think she was trying to be realistic about the state of older female artists in the music industry. She's been saying for years though that her musical journey is ''ending'', but it really hasn't--and hopefully it never will. :)
@lamb83 What does she mean by that exactly? I hope she doesn’t mean her age. She’s not even 50. Plenty of years to make great music ahead
